<!DOCTYPE html>

<html data-theme="light" lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- stylesheet van framework -->
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@picocss/pico@1.*/css/pico.min.css"> -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@1.8.6"></script>
    <title><%= it.title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Atkinson+Hyperlegible:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <svg 
        aria-hidden="true"
        focusable="false"
        viewBox="0 0 274 350" 
        fill="none" 
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path d="M122.5 23.5C133.833 81.5 153.1 222.8 139.5 324M45.5 146C68.5 139 172 120 210.5 133M118.916 1.62012C-18.4999 126 3.00024 255.228 3.00003 329.5C2.99995 356.676 271.302 354.783 271.475 319.737C271.648 284.691 276.546 103.781 118.916 1.62012Z" 
        stroke="black" 
        stroke-width="8" 
        stroke-linecap="round" 
        stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>

    <main class="container">
        <h1>Sinterklaasgedicht</h1>
        <p>Maak samen met de Digitale Stadsdichter jouw Sinterklaasgedicht. Vul de velden in en klik op de knop.</p>
        
        <form hx-post="/" hx-target="#output" hx-indicator="#spinner">
            <label>
                Voor wie is het gedicht?
                <input /*required*/ type="text" id="receiver" name="receiver" placeholder="Naam ontvanger"/>
            </label>

            <label>
                Wat is het cadeau?
                <input /*required*/ type="text" id="gift" name="gift" placeholder="Cadeautje"/>
            </label>

            <label>
                Verzin één of meer thema's voor het gedicht
                <input required type="text" id="theme" name="theme" placeholder="Thema"/>
            </label>

            <label>
                Wil je een beetje plagen met je gedicht?
                <select name="plagen">
                    <option value="niet">Niet plagen</option>
                    <option value="beetje">Een beetje plagen</option>
                    <option value="roast">Roasten</option>
                </select>
            </label>

            <label>
                Type
                <select name="type">
                    <option value="sinterklaasgedicht">Sinterklaasgedicht</option>
                    <option value="limerick">Limerick</option>
                    <option value="elevenie">Elevenie</option>
                    <option value="ollekebolleke">Ollekebolleke</option>
                    <option value="snelsonnet">Snelsonnet</option>
                    <option value="haiku">Haiku</option>
                    <option value="romantisch drama plot">Romantisch drama plot</option>
                    <option value="tragedie plot">Tragedie plot</option>
                    <option value="manifest">Manifest</option>
                    <option value="essay">Essay</option>
                    <option value="six word story">Six Word Story</option>
                    <option value="toneel opening tragedie">Toneel Opening Tragedie</option>
                    <option value="toneel opening komedie">Toneel Opening Komedie</option>
                </select>
            </label>

            <button type="submit">Schrijf gedicht</button>
        </form>

        <p id="spinner" class="htmx-indicator" aria-busy="true">Bezig met genereren, dit kan een minuut of langer duren...
            <iframe src="https://embed.lottiefiles.com/animation/60671" focusable="false"></iframe>
        </p>
        <p id="spinner-2" class="htmx-indicator" aria-busy="true">Bestaande tekst aan het aanpassen, dit kan een minuut of langer duren...
            <iframe src="https://embed.lottiefiles.com/animation/60671" focusable="false"></iframe>
        </p>

        <div id="output">
Beste Yuri, je bent zo slim en direct.
Met designen ben je altijd heel correct.
Grappig en aardig, dat is wie je bent.
Maar pas op voor obesitas, mijn goede vent.
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>

<style>
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'Atkinson Hyperlegible', sans-serif;
        transition: 300ms;
    }

    *:focus-visible {
        outline: 3px solid black!important;
    }

    body {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: #FFACDC;
    }

    svg {
        position: absolute;
        left: -15%;
        z-index: -1;
        height: 100%;
        mix-blend-mode: soft-light;
        opacity: 0.5;
    }

    main {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 40vw;
        min-width: 30em;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 64px;
        background-color: white;
    }

    h1 {
        width: 100%;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        text-align: center;
        color: #FF0000;
    }

    p {
        margin-top: 0;
        text-align: center;
    }

    form {
        display: grid;
        row-gap: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 3em;
    }

    label {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    input, select {
        height: 32px;
        margin-top: 8px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        border: 1px solid;
        text-indent: 8px;
    }

    button {
        padding: 8px;
        width: fit-content;
        background-color: #ffa0da;
        border: none;
        box-shadow: -4px 4px deeppink;
    }

    button:hover {
        background-color: deeppink;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px deeppink;

    }

    div {
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    iframe {
        height: 64px;
        border: none;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    .container a {
        display: none;
    }


</style>